description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1:

EIB Guest Host Michael Berry, from NewsRadio 740 KTRH in Houston, opens with Biden agreeing with "Let's go, Brandon!" Churchill stood tall. Biden's debacle in Afghanistan ends with just one brave soldier fired for speaking out. God bless you, old school moms standing up against CRT. Some heroes in medicine won't back down. January 6. Hillary and Democrats can say elections are rigged, but not Republicans.
